title: David Sedaris galore
description:
David Sedaris (born December 26, 1956) is an American humorist, comedian, author, radio contributor, and one of the funniest motherfuckers ever.

This torrent contains:

Dress Your Family in Corduroy and Denim (unabridged)
Let's Explore Diabetes With Owls (unabridged)
Live at Carnegie Hall
Holidays on Ice (abridged)
Me Talk Pretty One Day (unabridged)
When You Are Engulfed in Flames (unabridged)

plus a 40 minute interview, parts of Battle Fever and other goodies
